---
title: Creamy Garlic, Mushroom & Leek Pie with Filo Pastry & Roasted Potatoes
description: We love veggies, love garlic and we love filo pastry. So, let’s smash it all into a pie with a variety of seasonings like garlic and herb,
mushroom and of course a bit of lemon juice for an extra zap. Beware, everyone will be demanding more!

